{"tid":1489750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔良心小店介紹","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:07:57.000Z","uid":252636,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7136eec89db7d777119984c9fbad1d912b650316","tid":1489750,"uid":252636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:57:10.000Z","msg":"琴晚放工本身經過灣仔軒尼詩道搭車走嘅時候，咁就諗住試吓食飯碗越南粉先上車啦，點知嗰間老街執咗。轉手成AQ餐室。本身以為餐室啲嘢好普通。但呢間就唔同佢主力係買牛扒，而且啲牛扒真心好食過花園餐廳。而且，個湯仲好健康係零味精嘅羅宋湯。不過杯嘢飲就一般。唉，不過呢啲少店夜晚好靜租金又貴，我諗都唔會挨好耐。所以希望各位可以得閒經過去試吓啦。<br />\n<br />\n地址：灣仔軒尼詩道61號 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r7ZZHm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr7ZZHm1.png&h=7c5365d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c66e6012475c078d30e00dc48b60436489f8d16","tid":1489750,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"打手 扯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe6317dc23789b408c512e6d495c6fad97525cf","tid":1489750,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"How much"},{"pid":"8c082e5be427ffff9904c0f070c830c1c626e389","tid":1489750,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"笑了<br />\n<br />\n良心小店， 但你表達唔到有幾良心 <br />\n<br />\n想喺連登食人血饅頭， 你high大左 ?"},{"pid":"31451d47cfd7b0d2020a9c0feb0573eeb3852552","tid":1489750,"uid":177695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"良心去左邊?"},{"pid":"44658587c80405f17a2309c377f47268d9c92792","tid":1489750,"uid":295650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑了<br />\n<br />\n良心小店， 但你表達唔到有幾良心 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">想喺連登食人血饅頭， 你high大左 ?</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets